## Secrets Management

Secrets are managed using **{{if eq (printf "%s" .Secrets.Type) "sealed-secrets"}}Sealed Secrets{{else if eq (printf "%s" .Secrets.Type) "external-secrets"}}External Secrets Operator{{else}}SOPS{{end}}**. See [SECRETS.md](SECRETS.md) for details.

## Bootstrap Process

To bootstrap a new cluster:

```bash
# 1. Apply the bootstrap manifests
kubectl apply -k bootstrap/argocd/

# 2. Wait for ArgoCD to be ready
kubectl -n argocd rollout status deployment argocd-server

# 3. ArgoCD will pick up apps/_root.yaml and sync everything else
```
